    "body": "The EMAN2 package is very dependent on anaconda/miniconda (it is included in the cmake build process), and it seems very difficult to decouple it from the build.\r\n\r\nThis package uses the conda-based installer, which installs a bunch of dependencies alongside the package. Not sure how well these types of packages fit in Spack -- feedback is appreciated!",
